-- Aim Assist
• Enabled (toggle)
• Mode: Camlock / Mouse
• Keybind (default: C)
• AimMode: ClosestPart / ClosestPoint / Specific Part
• Target Part (e.g. UpperTorso)
• FOV (0–360)
• Smoothness control
• EasingStyle (Linear, Quad, Cubic, Sine, etc.)
• Deadzone + Deadzone radius (pixels)

-- Silent Aim
• Enabled (toggle)
• Mode: Target (needs lock) / FOV (independent)
• FOV for target selection
• Anti-Curve (2D/3D + angular limit)
• Closest Point prediction (Scalar/Generic)
• Client Bullet Redirection (weapon-specific)
• Prediction per weapon (e.g. 0.11)

-- Checks
• WallCheck
• UnlockOnWall (optional)
• StayOnTarget through walls
• Wall check throttle (anti-lag)
• Disable on reload
• Disable when knocked

-- Range
• Range limit toggle
• Max distance (studs)

-- Triggerbot
• Enabled (toggle)
• Trigger key (default: T)
• Wall check
• Trigger delay (ms)
• Prediction
• Blacklisted items (e.g. Knife)

-- Resolver
• Enabled (toggle)
• VelocityPredictor mode
• Custom prediction (e.g. 0.1314)
• Max lead distance
• Velocity history size
• Prediction strength & direction sensitivity

-- Visuals
• FOV circle (color + transparency)
• Snapline/tracer (color + thickness)

-- Movement
• Speed hack toggle
• WalkSpeed (e.g. 200)
• JumpPower (e.g. 200)
• Keybind (default: V)

-- No Spread
• Enabled (toggle)
• Spread amount (0 = none)

-- Rage - Orbit
• Strafe / Random teleport mode
• Distance, height, speed (strafe)
• Random radius + teleport delay (random)

-- Rage - BulletTP
• Bullet teleport on shot
• Spectate target option
• Target part (e.g. Head)

-- Misc
• Anti-Sit
• No Jump Cooldown
• Anti-Void (destroy height hack)
